wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好等用盡先叉<br />\n<br />\n叉緊電唔好用<br />\n<br />\n利申: 讀電"},{"pid":"74daff15104d12ee7d0e46e5cd0efd1c57744f30","tid":185271,"uid":5134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T00:34:33.000Z","msg":"去天才吧換電啦 保養期內底過80%免費換"},{"pid":"8356aef68ad774ff2a5f2c5d8ee63a241e73c6d9","tid":185271,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電都要就住差同用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好撚痴線，得返40%就話要叉，即係平時用得60%電。又話叉電唔好用電話，但部機又叉得慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />電蝕咗咪換過粒囉，有錢去apple store換，無錢去淘寶淘粒"},{"pid":"db5a4c3f11022f1723a45bd1bf80ddafcc9c43f1","tid":185271,"uid":19789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"不嬲都長差長用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c37cac5de0ce3c25cea9cc6125a202712d7f18","tid":185271,"uid":56537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:12:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7P8E38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7P8E38.jpg&h=e30b3987&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半年ip7+"},{"pid":"34bb085d4f9a2806632e7f956d4f23698e7ac04a","tid":185271,"uid":34168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33e092t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33e092t.jpg&h=1c1ada9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7+ 機齡4個月<br />\n20%開始充電 一充就充通宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634c962089d4de989fc1ad45585b70d9f0081f71","tid":185271,"uid":37731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:44:02.000Z","msg":"好似話用老翻線都會整壞舊電"},{"pid":"94189ec8c63d273d7998d477b6d8e1