.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c6bad3e3e977d0688cade9a3180c69c354683bd","tid":185271,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6s+<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/120318_5f1b2a53d4e8475b6fc45e115137eb12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F120318_5f1b2a53d4e8475b6fc45e115137eb12.jpg&h=19b2ef71&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有無applecare?<br />\n有就拎去換電啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47650c809b4565ebd570bf5e122930110f1d0a4c","tid":185271,"uid":28876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:35:31.000Z","msg":"用緊iphone7,用左4個月,上個月check仲係100%,琴日check得番97%"},{"pid":"94c9004ee1cab012adee14ecf30983cf6499fb5b","tid":185271,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:20:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用左大半年仲keep倒100既巴打可唔可以講下你地既使用習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n減少充電次數，每次都用到起碼見紅（本人習慣係5%以下）一叉就叉爆先用<br />\n<br />\n充電期間盡量唔用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有漏請補充<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人有打機，但係預到啱啱好，無電就唔玩</blockquote><br />\n認真?<br />\n但 Full charge 會扣 Charge cycle<br />\n一粒電通常只有大約 1000 次 charge cycle 既壽命"},{"pid":"39085793793feb2465ef4aec1f56a1a3575ffafe","tid":185271,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用左大半年仲keep倒100既巴打可唔可以講下你地既使用習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n減少充電次數，每次都用到起碼見紅（本人習慣係5%以下）一叉就叉爆先用<br />\n<br />\n充電期間盡量唔用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有漏請補充<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人有打機，但係預到啱啱好，無電就唔玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩今日問左個藍精靈 佢話最好係40-60%就差 唔好等少過20%果陣差 到底邊個先係對電池好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蘋果官方對鋰電池既解釋係最好保持電子流動<br />\n<br />\n一定唔會係少過 20% 先 charge<br />\n鋰電池太低電量未必 charge 得起"},{"pid":"37c00eeda3a79c83819d5e30db624079ff629607","tid":185271,"uid":35971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用左大半年仲keep倒100既巴打可唔可以講下你地既使用習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n減少充電次數，每次都用到起碼見紅（本人習慣係5%以下）一叉就叉爆先用<br />\n<br />\n充電期間盡量唔用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有漏請補充<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人有打機，但係預到啱啱好，無電就唔玩</blockquote><br />\n認真?<br />\n但 Full charge 會扣 Charge cycle<br />\n一粒電通常只有大約 1000 次 charge cycle 既壽命</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係差到99% 就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8406aa59ecd2cb0c7d76efba88362cfc8afee64b","tid":185271,"uid":13947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:29:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.apple.com/hk/batteries/why-lithium-ion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fbatteries%2Fwhy-lithium-ion%2F&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=277e2844\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.apple.com/hk/batteries/why-lithium-ion/</a><br />\n<br />\nApple官網有解釋~"},{"pid":"bd7ac03e875e609f0f75d64ccbe5578b0a39e479","tid":185271,"uid":35971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:30:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用左大半年仲keep倒100既巴打可唔可以講下你地既使用習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n減少充電次數，每次都用到起碼見紅（本人習慣係5%以下）一叉就叉爆先用<br />\n<br />\n充電期間盡量唔用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有漏請補充<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人有打機，但係預到啱啱好，無電就唔玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩今日問左個藍精靈 佢話最好係40-60%就差 唔好等少過20%果陣差 到底邊個先係對電池好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蘋果官方對鋰電池既解釋係最好保持電子流動<br />\n<br />\n一定唔會係少過 20% 先 charge<br />\n鋰電池太低電量未必 charge 得起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n藍精靈都講過20%可以差，但點先最好？"},{"pid":"a48ef0dcdb647dba7155f1afc01fd1e9aed38d1a","tid":185271,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:31:26.000Z","msg":"其實apple 係建議大家有機會叉就叉吓佢<br />\n唔好用晒啲電先叉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1381df9175b0e2dc5765f972ce115b3b69309071","tid":185271,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用左大半年仲keep倒100既巴打可唔可以講下你地既使用習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n減少充電次數，每次都用到起碼見紅（本人習慣係5%以下）一叉就叉爆先用<br />\n<br />\n充電期間盡量唔用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有漏請補充<br />\n<br />\n利申：本人有打機，但係預到啱啱好，無電就唔玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁岩今日問左個藍精靈 佢話最好係40-60%就差 唔好等少過20%果陣差 到底邊個先係對電池好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蘋果官方對鋰電池既解釋係最好保持電子流動<br />\n<br />\n一定唔會係少過 20% 先 charge<br />\n鋰電池太低電量未必 charge 得起</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n藍精靈都講過20%可以差，但點先最好？</blockquote><br />\n樓上巴打貼條官方 link 都解釋曬<br />\n最緊要係唔好用個 charge cycle"},{"pid":"61b626242aee4e8782709d91680abac5da8859b3","tid":185271,"uid":24420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/203534_0629159b704d3f5e5fddbe7a0c03bc86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F203534_0629159b704d3f5e5fddbe7a0c03bc86.jpg&h=ba761e20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n6+接近兩年"},{"pid":"cd98306c37df73c2b2adee33edb687283f32e4d2","tid":185271,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E236e1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE236e1N.png&h=1be7d3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7+ 1月尾出機到依家，用12W牛叉"},{"pid":"f0527c09c6240adceb25181cb47edadad006f15f","tid":185271,"uid":96457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>6s+<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/120318_5f1b2a53d4e8475b6fc45e115137eb12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F120318_5f1b2a53d4e8475b6fc45e115137eb12.jpg&h=19b2ef71&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n到底叉爆電可以用到幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548813b3e8cac288828e5c26a83e92ae10308e3d","tid":185271,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實apple 係建議大家有機會叉就叉吓佢<br />\n唔好用晒啲電先叉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有得叉就好叉<br />\n最好係保持係40-80%<br />\n電池損耗較少<br />\n落到低電量再叉滿好快打柴<br />\n當然apple 有軟件控制<br />\n但鋰電池始終都係鋰電池<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n300次loop 跌20%<br />\n1000次打柴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他牌子都係咁講<br />\n任何鋰電池都岩用<br />\n<br />\n充電時間<br />\n<br />\n想要延長電池壽命，勿讓電池過度的充放電,充電時建議充滿約 60% 即可；放電時建議別讓電量耗盡，甚至低於20%會傷害鋰電池。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n電池循環壽命<br />\n<br />\n1. 鋰離子（Li-ion）因其化學特性，電池容量會隨著電池使用時間做線性式的衰減，此為正常現象。<br />\n<br />\n2. 鋰離子（Li-ion）電池的壽命週期約在300次循環~500次循環之間。正常使用情況下與環境溫度( 25℃ )左右，鋰離子電池可以預估正常充放電使用300次循環( 或大約一年 )，之後電池容量將降至電池初始容量的 80%。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asus.com/hk/support/faq/1009546\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asus.com%2Fhk%2Fsupport%2Ffaq%2F1009546&d=kJJ5Rp8RNWWpGPQirZinA3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=677ce41c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asus.com/hk/support/faq/1009546</a>"},{"pid":"f64fc9684e9e54452762ac5972fa61ecb3edd3cc","tid":185271,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T12:52:28.000Z","msg":"手機電池充電的整個過程包括快速充電、連續式充電、涓流充電三個階段。經過前兩個階段之後，雖然系統電量顯示100%，但實際上電池並未真正達到飽和狀態。此時剩餘的容量只能靠微小的脈衝電流補充，這個階段通常需要30-40分鐘。"},{"pid":"fef3bfd995937d38d723dda4e7c2081261e31b46","tid":185271,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:02:39.000Z","msg":"只要使用apple的官方電源，充滿後會變成直接使用電源模式，不存在 iPhone 6/iPhone 6 Plus過充的問題。鋰電池的充電過程就是前80%採用快速充電2小時即可完成，後20%採用連續補充充電也要2小時只要使用apple的官方電源，充滿後會變成直接使用電源模式，不存在 iPhone 6/iPhone 6 Plus過充的問題。鋰電池的充電過程就是前80%採用快速充電2小時即可完成，後20%採用連續補充充電也要2小時。<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好開機叉過夜<br />\n都係好快打柴<br />\n滿電後跌5%再叉<br />\n叉完又跌，跌完又叉<br />\n每日都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 快死幾個%"},{"pid":"b84d627a2f0f02cdc44f5ea8f34a88564bc71fec","tid":185271,"uid":64264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:07:29.000Z","msg":"用咩app可以check?"},{"pid":"40d62d0ba17d597b3e5ec1e9feb238532e621eeb","tid":185271,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:11:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用咩app可以check?</blockquote><br />\nBattery Life"},{"pid":"00fea5650455ff18f745d3b81fc3c50cd59b1b28","tid":185271,"uid":18323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"我iPhone 6 Plus 用咗兩年半仲有90%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/211301_ef7d467b57c17f73e590a45144ad924b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F211301_ef7d467b57c17f73e590a45144ad924b.jpg&h=34d6e168&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c96720c1e406ce5fb4b3b770ce0ef8e3902908f","tid":185271,"uid":87186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/05/211702_20b1bd7d12b77614823a8a790a89417c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F05%2F211702_20b1bd7d12b77614823a8a790a89417c.jpg&h=964df03e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n7+ 10月頭出到依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日叉住電用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}